  "description": "<a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543807/\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201311/af160dff7d2f445880e606b1dd81f5d4.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tIt was just announced that Robert Pattinson will be starring in the upcoming film The Lost City of Z, according to The Wrap.据The Warp报道，罗伯特&middot;帕丁森宣布加盟《迷失Z城》。<br />\n\tThe 27-year-old English actor will be joined in the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/flick\" target=\"_blank\">flick</a> by Benedict Cumberbatch, who will be playing the role of British explorer Percy Fawcett.这位27岁的英国男演员将和本尼迪克特&middot;康伯巴奇一起出演，卷福在剧中扮演英国探险家珀西&middot;福西特。<br />\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201311/d9e88fb7dd12481fb704a4b6098db5fd.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tThe film - which is being directed by James Gray - is based on the novel by David Grann, and will be produced by Brad Pitt's company, Plan B. Robert&lsquo;s role in the film is currently unknown.本片由詹姆斯&middot;格雷执导，根据大卫&middot;古兰同名小说改编，由布拉德&middot;皮特的Plan B公司制作。罗伯特在影片中的角色暂时未透露。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543807/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543807\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543801/\">11.11又来了：光棍们悲剧大盘点</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p542313/\">关于笑声你可能不知道的9个好处</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543701/\">萌视频：美国小朋友对同性恋的看法</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en